INSTALL:
========

Install git, nodejs, node-express, npm and mongodb

Clone repository:
  git clone https://github.com/vesapehkonen/jatrailmap.git

Install node modules:
  cd jatrailmap/nodejs
  npm install

Default request body size is 102400 bytes, change it to bigger
add line 
  limit = 1024 * 1024 * 50;
to file node_modules/body-parser/node_modules/raw-body/index.js, before line 33.

RUN:
========

Start server
npm start

Start browser with an address http://localhost:3000
